rgin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit;\">Power Camera</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: justify;\">Whether you are installing or troubleshooting cameras, SecuriTEST IP supports all your power requirements for IP and analogue cameras.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: justify;\">No need for separate power injectors &ndash; SecuriTEST IP includes the following power outputs:</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2338 alignnone\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto; max-width: 99%; border-style: none; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"SecuriTEST IP CCTV Tester 2\" src=\"https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power1_400_en.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" srcset=\"https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power1_400_en.jpg 400w, https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power1_400_en-300x170.jpg 300w\" alt=\"power1 400 en\" width=\"400\" height=\"226\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2347 alignnone\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto; max-width: 99%; border-style: none; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"SecuriTEST IP CCTV Tester 3\" src=\"https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power2_400_en.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" srcset=\"https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power2_400_en.jpg 400w, https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power2_400_en-300x170.jpg 300w\" alt=\"power2 400 en\" width=\"400\" height=\"226\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2356 alignnone entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto; max-width: 99%; border-style: none; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"SecuriTEST IP CCTV Tester 4\" src=\"https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power3_400_en.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" srcset=\"https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power3_400_en.jpg 400w, https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power3_400_en-300x170.jpg 300w\" alt=\"power3 400 en\" width=\"400\" height=\"226\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power3_400_en.jpg 400w, https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power3_400_en-300x170.jpg 300w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.trend-networks.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/power3_400_en.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n\r\n', NULL, NULL, 'service_icon_1730878313.png', NULL, 'product_photo_1730878313.png', '17', '2024-11-06 14:31:53', '2024-11-06 14:31:53'),
(50, 'Advantech EKI-7554SI', NULL, NULL, '4FE+2FE SC Single-mode Managed Ethernet Switch, -40~75℃', NULL, NULL, '<h4 class=\"product-name\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --porto-h1-ff: \'Roboto\'; --porto-h1-fw: 700; --porto-h1-fs: 36px; --porto-h1-lh: 44px; --porto-h1-ls: 0; --porto-h1-color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 32px; font: var(--porto-h1-fst,normal) var(--porto-h1-fw,700) var(--porto-h1-fs,2.6em)/var(--porto-h1-lh,44px) var(--porto-h1-ff,var(--porto-body-ff)),sans-serif; color: var(--porto-h1-color,var(--porto-heading-color)); letter-spacing: var(--porto-h1-ls,-.05em);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">EKI-7554SI&rsquo;s</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">&nbsp;Introduction:</span></span></span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"product-overview\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9; text-align: justify;\">Both the<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;EKI-7554SI&nbsp;</span>and EKI-7559SI/MI support two&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/\">SC type</a></span>&nbsp;Fiber ports, EKI-7554SI four Fast&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Ethernet ports</span>&nbsp;and EKI-7559SI/MI can support up to eight Fast Ethernet ports.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />To create reliability in your network, the EKI-7554SI&nbsp;come equipped with a proprietary redundant&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">network</span>&nbsp;protocol &mdash; X-Ring Pro that was developed by&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://www.advantech.com/en-eu\">Advantech</a></span>, which provides<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />users with an easy way to establish a redundant Ethernet<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;network&nbsp;</span>with ultra high-speed recovery time less than 20ms. Furthermore, EKI-7554SI&nbsp;also supports many advanced<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\" />network standards to optimize network performance, ease maintenance issues, and secure network safety.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --porto-h2-ff: \'Roboto\'; --porto-h2-fw: 700; --porto-h2-fs: 30px; --porto-h2-lh: 40px; --porto-h2-ls: normal; --porto-h2-color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.4286em; color: var(--porto-h2-color,var(--porto-heading-color)); letter-spacing: var(--porto-h2-ls,-.05em);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\">EKI-7554SI&rsquo;s Key Features:</span></span></h4>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">2 x SC-type fiber ports, plus 4 Fast Ethernet ports</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">Redundancy: X-Ring (high-speed recovery time10ms), RSTP/STP (802.1w/1D)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">Management: Web, Telnet, Serial Console, SNMP</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">Control: VLAN/GVRP, QoS, IGMP Snooping/Query, LACP, Rate Limit</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">Security: IP/MAC, port binding, DHCP Server, IP access list, 802.1X, SNMPv3</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">Diagnostic: Port Statistic, Port Mirroring, RMON, Trap, Email Alert, Syslog</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">Dual 12 ~ 48 VDC power input and 1 Relay Output</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh); margin-bottom: 0px;\">Supports wide operating temperature -40 ~ 75&deg; C</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"posted_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\">Categories:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/industrial-data-communications/\" rel=\"tag\">Industrial Data Communications</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/industrial-data-communications/industrial-ethernet-switches/\" rel=\"tag\">Industrial Ethernet Switches</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"tagged_as\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tags:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/ethernet-switch/\" rel=\"tag\">Ethernet Switch</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/managed-switch/\" rel=\"tag\">Managed Switch</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/switch/\" rel=\"tag\">switch</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"yith-wcbr-brands\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-top: 15px;\">Brand:&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; font-weight: 400; color: #777777;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-brands/advantech/\" rel=\"tag\">ADVANTECH</a></span></span></p>', NULL, NULL, 'service_icon_1731307448.png', NULL, 'product_photo_1731307448.png', '13', '2024-11-11 13:44:08', '2024-11-11 14:06:24');
