(51, 'Advantech EKI-7720G-4FI', NULL, NULL, '16GE+4G SFP Managed Ethernet Switch, -40~75℃', NULL, NULL, '<h4 class=\"product-name\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --porto-h2-ff: \'Roboto\'; --porto-h2-fw: 700; --porto-h2-fs: 30px; --porto-h2-lh: 40px; --porto-h2-ls: normal; --porto-h2-color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.4286em; color: var(--porto-h2-color,var(--porto-heading-color)); letter-spacing: var(--porto-h2-ls,-.05em);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">EKI-7720G-4FI&rsquo;s</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">&nbsp;Introduction:</span></span></span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"product-overview\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\">The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product/advantech-eki-7720g-4fi/\">EKI-7720G-4F</a></span>&nbsp;and EKI-7720G-4FI provide users with abundant port options for connecting to various device types with 16 Gigabit Ethernet ports and 4 SFP (mini-GBIC) ports.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />These switches are embedded with Advantech&rsquo;s IXM function, which can benefit users with fast deployment and can dramatically save on engineering time and costs. The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://www.advantech.com/en/products/1-2mljzp/eki-7720g-4fi/mod_976ef035-9d39-4f70-b1ed-de7f715523