(92, 'Antaira LMP-0602-M-24-V2', NULL, NULL, '6-Port Industrial PoE+ Managed Ethernet Switch, w/4*10/100Tx (30W/Port) and 2*100Fx Multi-Mode 2Km, 12~36VDC Power Input; Version 2 Hardware , STD: -10°C to 70°C', NULL, NULL, '<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Introduction:</span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\">Antaira Technologies&rsquo; LMP-0602-M-24-V2 series is a 6-port industrial PoE+ managed Ethernet switch embedded with 4*10/100Tx Ethernet ports that support IEEE802.3at/af for a maximum of 30W/port and 2*100Fx fiber connections. The LMP-0602-M-24-V2 is a fully manageable Layer 2 Ethernet switch that is pre-loaded with a user-friendly web management console design. It supports the ring network redundancy function using the market&rsquo;s open standard ITU-T G.8032 Ethernet Ring Protection Switch (ERPS) protocol that has a 50ms network recovery time. The advanced network filtering and security functions, such as IGMP, VLAN, QoS, SNMP, RMON, Modbus TCP, and 802.1X/HTTPS/SSH/SSL increase determinism and improve network management for remote SCADA systems or control networks. The LMP-0602-M-24-V2 series is IP30 rated and DIN-rail mountable. There are also two wide operating temperature models for either a standard temperature range (STD: -10&deg;C to 70&deg;C) . It also provides high EFT and ESD protection for industrial networking applications, such as power/utility, water wastewater, oil/gas/mining, factory automation, security surveillance, ITS and any other outdoor or harsh environment.</p>\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Key Features:</span></h4>\r\n<ul style=\"box-s