ugh E-mail, Relay Output</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;Operating Temp &ndash;STD: -10~70&deg;C</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh); margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;5-Year Warranty</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"posted_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\">Category:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/industrial-data-communications/industrial-ethernet-switches/\" rel=\"tag\">Industrial Ethernet Switches</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"tagged_as\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tags:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/antaira/\" rel=\"tag\">Antaira</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/din-rail/\" rel=\"tag\">Din-rail</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/ethernet/\" rel=\"tag\">Ethernet</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/factory-automation/\" rel=\"tag\">Factory Automation</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/gigabit/\" rel=\"tag\">GIGABIT</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"bo