(171, 'Ruckus H350 Access Point', NULL, NULL, 'Entry-Level Wall-Mounted Wi-Fi 6 2×2:2 Indoor Access Point with 1.8 Gbps max rate, Switch and Embedded IoT', NULL, NULL, '<h4 class=\"product-name\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --porto-h2-ff: \'Roboto\'; --porto-h2-fw: 700; --porto-h2-fs: 30px; --porto-h2-lh: 40px; --porto-h2-ls: normal; --porto-h2-color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.4286em; color: var(--porto-h2-color,var(--porto-heading-color)); letter-spacing: var(--porto-h2-ls,-.05em);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">H350 &rsquo;s</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">&nbsp;Introduction:</span></span></span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\">In hotels, apartment buildings, and other multi-dwelling structures, wireless connectivity can carry a hefty price tag. You need to connect a wide range of wired devices &ndash; IPTV set-top boxes, IP phones, networked minibars &ndash; IoT devices like smart locks and sensors &ndash; while delivering a great wireless experience for guests. The RUCKUS&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product/ruckus-h350/\">H350</a></span>&nbsp;wall-mounted access point, IoT gateway, and Ethernet switch make it easy to support in-room connectivity requirements. It starts with RUCKUS patented Wi-Fi optimization intelligence to deliver the industry&rsquo;s highest-performing wireless connectivity. Combine that with two-ports of Gigabit Ethernet to connect in-room wired devices, without extra cabling and add supports for Zigbee&reg; or Bluetooth&reg; Low Energy. Put it all in a sleek, low-profile design that can be discretely installed over a standard electrical outlet.The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://www.commscope.com/\">RUCKUS&reg;</a></span>&nbsp;H350 delivers consistent, reliable Wi-Fi 6 (802.11ax) wireless networking without breaking the bank. The AP features the patented RUCKUS technologies for performance optimization and interference mitigation found in our premier access points, delivering superior user experiences. But it provides them in an entry-level product built for smaller venues with limited device diversity.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"posted_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\">Categories:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/wireless-communications/access-point/\" rel=\"tag\">Access Point</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/wireless-communications/\" rel=\"tag\">Wireless Communications</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"tagged_as\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tags:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/enterprise-wifi/\" rel=\"tag\">Enterprise WiFi</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !i