(176, 'Ruckus R350 Access Point', NULL, NULL, 'Entry-Level Wi-Fi 6 2×2:2 Indoor Access Point with 1.8 Gbps max rate and IoT ready', NULL, NULL, '<h4 class=\"product-name\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --porto-h2-ff: \'Roboto\'; --porto-h2-fw: 700; --porto-h2-fs: 30px; --porto-h2-lh: 40px; --porto-h2-ls: normal; --porto-h2-color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.4286em; color: var(--porto-h2-color,var(--porto-heading-color)); letter-spacing: var(--porto-h2-ls,-.05em);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">R350 &rsquo;s</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">&nbsp;Introduction:</span></span></span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\">Smaller locations can face big-time demands on their wireless infrastructure. Whether working out of a small office or connecting to a public hotspot, users are often still accessing the same high-bandwidth applications and content they&rsquo;d consume anywhere else. And they expect strong, reliable connectivity. How can you provide it without breaking the bank? the RUKCUS&reg;&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product/ruckus-r350/\">R350</a></span>&nbsp;Wi-Fi 6, IoT ready indoor access point delivers 802.11ax wireless connectivity combined with all the&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://www.commscope.com/\">RUCKUS</a></span>&nbsp;patented technologies for performance optimization and interference mitigation found in our premier access points. Get industry-leading Wi-Fi 6 performance in a package designed for smaller venues&mdash;with a price tag to match.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"posted_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\">Categories:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/wireless-communications/access-point/\" rel=\"tag\">Access Point</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/wireless-communications/\" rel=\"tag\">Wireless Communications</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"tagged_as\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tags:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/enterprise-wifi/\" rel=\"tag\">Enterprise WiFi</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/indoor-access-point/\" rel=\"tag\">Indoor Access Point</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/wireless/\" rel=\"tag\">wireless</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/wireless-networking/\" rel=\"tag\">Wireless Networking