(177, 'Ruckus R550 Access Point', NULL, NULL, 'Mid-Tier Wi-Fi 6 2×2:2 Indoor Access Point with 1.8 Gbps max rate and Embedded IoT', NULL, NULL, '<h2 class=\"product-name\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --porto-h2-ff: \'Roboto\'; --porto-h2-fw: 700; --porto-h2-fs: 30px; --porto-h2-lh: 40px; --porto-h2-ls: normal; --porto-h2-color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.4286em; color: var(--porto-h2-color,var(--porto-heading-color)); letter-spacing: var(--porto-h2-ls,-.05em);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">R550 &rsquo;s</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">&nbsp;Introduction:</span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\">Wi-Fi capacity requirements in classrooms, office spaces, and medium-size venues are rising due to the increase in the number of Wi-Fi connected devices. An increase in bandwidth requirements for applications and an ever-growing assortment of IoT devices puts further strain on already stretched Wi-Fi networks. The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product/ruckus-r550/\">R550</a></span>&nbsp;access point (AP) with the latest Wi-Fi 6 (802.11 ax) technology delivers the ideal combination of increased capacity, improved coverage and affordability in dense environments. This access point is our mid- range dual-band, dual-concurrent AP that supports four spatial streams (2&times;2:2 in 2.4GHz/5GHz). The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://www.commscope.com/\">RUCKUS</a></span>&nbsp;R550 supports peak data rates of up to 1774 Mbps and efficiently manages up to 512 clients connections.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"posted_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\">Categories:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/wireless-communications/access-point/\" rel=\"tag\">Access Point</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/wireless-communications/\" rel=\"tag\">Wireless Communications</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"tagged_as\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tags:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/enterprise-wifi/\" rel=\"tag\">Enterprise WiFi</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/indoor-access-point/\" rel=\"tag\">Indoor Access Point</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/wireless/\" rel=\"tag\">wireless</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/wireless-networking/\" rel=\"tag\">Wireless Networking</a></span> &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"yith-wcbr-brands\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-top: 15px;\">Brand:&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; font-weight: 400; color: #777777;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-brands/ruckus/\" rel=\"tag\">Ruckus</a></span></span></p>', NULL, NULL, 'service_icon_1731490052.jpg', NULL, 'product_photo_1731490052.jpg', '19', '2024-11-13 16:27:32', '2024-11-13 16:28:45'),
(178, 'Antaira LMX-0600', NULL, NULL, '6-Port Industrial Managed Switch, with 6*10/100Tx,12~48VDC, STD: -10 to 70C', NULL, NULL, '<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Introduction:</span></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\">Antaira LMX-0600 series is a 6-port industrial managed Ethernet switch that is embedded with 6*10/100Tx fast Ethernet ports. This series is a fully manageable industrial Ethernet switch pre-loaded with standard Layer 2 network management software, and supports a user friendly web console interface for easy configuration.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\" />LMX-0600 series is IP30 rated, DIN-rail mountable, and has two wide operating temperature models for either a standard temperature range ( STD: -10&deg;C to 70&deg;C). It also provides high EFT and ESD protection for any industrial networking application within factory automation, ITS, power/utility, water wastewater, and any other outdoor or harsh environment.</p>\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Key Features:</span></h4>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;Supports 6*10/100Tx Fast Ethernet Ports</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;Network Redundancy support: RSTP, and G.8032 ERPS (Recovery Time 50ms)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;Configuration: Web Console, Telnet, CLI Command</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;Supports IGMP v1/v2, up to 256 Groups</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;Supports QoS (IEEE802.1p) and CoS/ToS</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;Supports IEEE802.1Q VLAN, SNMP v1/v2c</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;System Warning Setting for Automatic Warning through E-Mail</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;Redundant Power Input Design &ndash; 12~48VDC</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;Housing: Metal IP 30 Rated; DIN-Rail and Wall Mount Support</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh);\">&nbsp;Operating Temperature &ndash; STD: -10 to 70C</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: var(--porto-body-lh); margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;5-Year Warranty</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"posted_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\">Categories:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/industrial-data-communications/\" rel=\"tag\">Industrial Data Communications</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/industrial-data-communications/industrial-ethernet-switches/\" rel=\"tag\">Industrial Ethernet Switches</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"tagged_as\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tags:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/antaira/\" rel=\"tag\">Antaira</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/din-rail/\" rel=\"tag\">Din-rail</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/ethernet/\" rel=\"tag\">Ethernet</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/factory-automation/\" rel=\"tag\">Factory Automation</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/industrial-ethernet-switch/\" rel=\"tag\">industrial Ethernet switch</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/its/\" rel=\"tag\">ITS</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/its-traffic-monitoring-systems/\" rel=\"tag\">ITS-traffic monitoring systems</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/managed/\" rel=\"tag\">Managed</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/oil-gas/\" rel=\"tag\">Oil &amp; Gas</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/power-utility/\" rel=\"tag\">Power Utility</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/rj45/\" rel=\"tag\">RJ45</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"yith-wcbr-brands\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-top: 15px;\">Brand:&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; font-weight: 400; color: #777777;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-brands/antaira-products/\" rel=\"tag\">Antaira</a></span></span></p>', NULL, NULL, 'service_icon_1731490161.png', NULL, 'product_photo_1731490161.png', '13', '2024-11-13 16:29:21', '2024-11-13 16:29:48'),
(179, 'Ruckus R750 Access Point', NULL, NULL, 'Very High-Performance Wi-Fi 6 4×4:4 Indoor Access Point with 3.5 Gbps max rate and Embedded IoT', NULL, NULL, '<h4 class=\"product-name\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --porto-h2-ff: \'Roboto\'; --porto-h2-fw: 700; --porto-h2-fs: 30px; --porto-h2-lh: 40px; --porto-h2-ls: normal; --porto-h2-color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.4286em; color: var(--porto-h2-color,var(--porto-heading-color)); letter-spacing: var(--porto-h2-ls,-.05em);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">R750&rsquo;s</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">&nbsp;Introduction:</span></span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\">The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product/ruckus-r750/\">R750</a></span>&nbsp;is based on the latest Wi-Fi 6 standard and bridges the performance gap from &lsquo;gigabit&rsquo; Wi-Fi to &lsquo;multi-gigabit&rsquo; Wi-Fi in support of the insatiable demand for better and faster Wi-Fi. The R750 is the first ever Wi-Fi 6 AP to be granted Wi-Fi CERTIFIED 6 status by the Wi-Fi Alliance. As part of Wi-Fi Alliance&rsquo;s testbed, this access point validates other devices for Wi-Fi CERTIFIED 6 interoperability certification. The RUCKUS access point makes it easy to deliver reliable, secure, high-performance connectivity in transit hubs, auditoriums, conference centers and other high traffic indoor spaces. The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://www.commscope.com/\">RUCKUS</a></span>&nbsp;R750 is our high-end dual-band, dual-concurrent Wi-Fi 6 AP that supports 8 spatial streams (4&times;4:4 in 5GHz, 4&times;4:4 in 2.4GHz). The R750, with OFDMA and MU-MIMO capabilities, efficiently manages up to 1024 client connections with increased capacity, improved coverage and performance in ultra-high dense environments. Also, wireless requirements within enterprises are expanding beyond Wi-Fi with Bluetooth&reg; Low Energy, Zigbee and many other non-Wi-Fi wireless technologies. Enterprises need a unified platform to eliminate network silos. The RUCKUS AP portfolio is equipped to solve these challenges through wireless convergence. This access point is also easy to manage through RUCKUS physical and virtual cloud management options.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"posted_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\">Categories:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/wireless-communications/access-point/\" rel=\"tag\">Access Point</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-category/wireless-communications/\" rel=\"tag\">Wireless Communications</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"tagged_as\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tags:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product-tag/dual-band/\" rel=\"tag\">Dual-Band</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #777777; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; 