(183, 'Ruckus R850 Access Point', NULL, NULL, 'Ultra High-Performance Wi-Fi 6 8×8:8 Indoor Access Point with 5.9 Gbps max rate and Embedded IoT', NULL, NULL, '<h4 class=\"product-name\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --porto-h2-ff: \'Roboto\'; --porto-h2-fw: 700; --porto-h2-fs: 30px; --porto-h2-lh: 40px; --porto-h2-ls: normal; --porto-h2-color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.4286em; color: var(--porto-h2-color,var(--porto-heading-color)); letter-spacing: var(--porto-h2-ls,-.05em);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">R850 &rsquo;s</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">&nbsp;Introduction:</span></span></span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\">The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product/ruckus-r850/\">R850</a></span>&nbsp;is based on the latest Wi-Fi standard, Wi-Fi 6 and bridges the performance gap from &lsquo;gigabit&rsquo; Wi-Fi to &lsquo;multi-gigabit&rsquo; Wi-Fi in support of the insatiable demand for better and faster Wi-Fi.This access point makes it easy to deliver reliable, secure, ultra-high-performance connectivity to large enterprises, public venues, convention centers, and other challenging environments.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"http://commscope.com/\">RUCKUS<