(189, 'Ruckus T750 Access Point', NULL, NULL, 'Very High-Performance Wi-Fi 6 4×4:4 Outdoor Access Point with 3.5 Gbps max rate', NULL, NULL, '<h4 class=\"product-name\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --porto-h2-ff: \'Roboto\'; --porto-h2-fw: 700; --porto-h2-fs: 30px; --porto-h2-lh: 40px; --porto-h2-ls: normal; --porto-h2-color: #000000; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1.4286em; color: var(--porto-h2-color,var(--porto-heading-color)); letter-spacing: var(--porto-h2-ls,-.05em);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">T750 &rsquo;s</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 30px;\">&nbsp;Introduction:</span></span></span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.005em; line-height: 1.9;\">Outdoor locations such as stadiums, arenas can have the most demanding wireless requirements due to high client density. The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: none !important;\" href=\"https://maktonet.com/product/ruckus-t750/\">T750</a></span>&nbsp;access point (AP), based on the latest Wi-Fi 6 standard, brings in multi-gigabit Wi-Fi to support the ever raising expectation for highest quality of service from the users. T750 is IP-67 rated to withstand the rigors of outdoor deployments. The access point is our high-end dual-band, dual-concurrent Wi-Fi 6 AP that supports 8 spatial streams (4&times;4:4 in 5GHz, 4&times;4:4 in 2.4GHz). The T750, with OFDMA and MU-MIMO capabilities, efficiently manages up to 1,024 client connections with increased capacity, improved coverage and performance in ultra-high dense envi