(253, 'UbiBot WS1', NULL, NULL, 'Cloud-based WiFi temperature, humidity, ambient light data logger and monitoring device', NULL, NULL, '<p>The UbiBot WS1 is an advanced all-in-one IoT sensor built with industrial grade components. The WS1 measures temperature, humidity, ambient light, vibration.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">The WS1 allows you to wirelessly monitor your environment in real-time and gives you remote access to your data wherever you are in the world. All the data is automatically synchronised to our big data platform via WiFi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Our cloud-based IoT platform offers advanced data analysis and management. It also allows you to setup real-time notifications - if a metric goes outside the range you specify, the platform will notify you through the app, by email or other methods, allowing you to respond promptly before costly damage happens. The IoT platform gives users access to both the real-time data and history via our mobile app or on any browser. We are now working with IFTTT (if this then that), allowing you to build custom link with other smart devices.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Switch the temp unit &deg;F/&deg;C and user calibration is available. The device can store over 300,000 records in its internal memory, which can protect your data against network failure. Even if the network fails, the UbiBot WS1 still stores readings, thus ensuring there are no gaps in the data history.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">The data sync interval can be set by you. This allows you to balance battery life against frequency of data capture. With the default data sync interval of 15 minutes the device has a battery life of up to 4- 6 months using 2 AA alkaline batteries. Power-supply using Micro-USB is supported. You can check the battery voltage of the device remotely and set up rules to be notified when low-battery, network failure or sensor reading exceeds the setting range. Available rule alerts include Email, APP, SMS, Phone Call, HTTP API. Please note, charges may apply to SMS text and voice call alert modes. These two modes cost the balance of the credits in your account.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">No subscription is needed. Free 200MB Cloud Storage enough to store data over 2 years on default settings. Export the data to CSV or PDF without extra charge.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 12px;\">Temperature :&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">-20℃ to 60℃ ( -4℉ to 140℉)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 12px;\">Humidity :&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">10% to 90%, No condensation</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 12px;\">Light :&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">0-83k lux</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 12px;\">Accuracy :&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">Temperature &plusmn;0.2 ℃, humidity &plusmn;2%, ambient light &plusmn;2%</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Data communications :&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">WiFi</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">WiFi : 2.4GHz, channels 1-13 (5GHz WiFi NOT supported)</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Certification :&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">CE, RoHS, FCC, RCM, IC certificates</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Memory :&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">300,000 sensor records</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\">External Probe :&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Supports DS18B20 probe (optional extra)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'product_banner_1733122595.jpg', NULL, 'product_1733122595.jpg', '11', '2024-12-02 13:52:32', '2024-12-02 14:17:31'),
(254, 'UbiBot WS1 Pro', NULL, NULL, 'Cloud-based WiFi data logger for temperature, humidity, and ambient light monitoring with a 4.4” LCD screen (Optional with SIM connection)', NULL, NULL, '<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">It have two versions</h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- WiFi</h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- WiFi and SIM</h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">UbiBot&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; position: relative; font-size: 7.8px; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">&reg;</span>&nbsp;WS1 Pro is a cloud-based environmental monitoring data logger. WS1 Pro&rsquo; built-in sensors detect and measure temperature, humidity, and ambient light. Via a WiFi connection, it syncs data to the UbiBot IoT cloud platform, which gives you access to both real-time and historical data through the UbiBot App or Web Console platform anywhere in the world and allows you to receive real-time alerts.</h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">With a 4.4&rdquo; high-quality LCD screen, it displays current environmental conditions and shows any alerts and notifications in real time.</h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">It has two on-board USB ports; with splitters, it can connect 2 x DS18B20 Temperature Probe and 1 x RS485 probe at a time, and can be connected simultaneously to the external power source.</h6>\r\n<h6 style