(266, 'Ubibot External CO2 Probe', NULL, NULL, 'CO2 concentration measuring & monitoring 24/7 with real-time alerts', NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">UbiBot CO2 Sensors - UB-CO2-P1 and UB-CO2-P3 The UbiBot CO2 sensors are designed for high-precision CO2 monitoring, suitable for a range of environments, from industrial applications to office spaces. Both the UB-CO2-P1 and UB-CO2-P3 models provide robust stability, long-range communication, and seamless integration with systems using the Modbus RTU protocol over an RS485 interface.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">UB-CO2-P1:</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">High-Precision Monitoring: Measures CO2 concentrations from 400 to 10,000 ppm (up to 40,000 ppm), plus temperature (-40&deg;C to 70&deg;C) and humidity (0~100%RH).</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Versatile Use: Ideal for agricultural greenhouses, industrial applications, smart buildings, and environments requiring comprehensive monitoring.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Advanced Accuracy: CO2 accuracy of &plusmn;(30ppm+3%), making it highly reliable in fluctuating environmental conditions.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">All-in-One Solution: Tracks CO2, temperature, and humidity in a single device, offering a complete monitoring solution.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">UB-CO2-P3:</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Focused CO2 Monitoring: Measures CO2 concentrations between 400 and 2,000 ppm (up to 10,000 ppm), specifically designed for environments where only CO2 data is needed.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Precision and Simplicity: CO2 accuracy of &plusmn;(40ppm+3%), perfect for ventilation systems, office environments, libraries, and laboratories.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Cost-Effective Solution: Focuses solely on CO2 measurement, making it an affordable yet precise option for standard environments.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Key Features for Both Models:</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Durable and Stable: Both models offer strong anti-interference performance, ensuring consistent and reliable readings even in challenging environments.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Long-Range Communication: With an RS485 interface, both sensors support communication distances of up to 1200 meters, ideal for large-scale applications.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Seamless Integration: Fully compatible with the Modbus RTU protocol, making it easy to integrate into existing monitoring systems.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #585858; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Flexible Power Options: Both models operate on DC 5/12V, allowing for easy installation across a range of setups.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'service_icon_1733130279.png', NULL, 'product_photo_1733130279.png', '11', '2024-12-02 16:04:39', '2024-12-02 16:04:39'),
